  '901': 'Messy Mullet: modern mullet with deliberately tousled, piece-y texture on top and front (5-8cm), scissor-cut tight sides, and distinctly longer textured back sections falling past the collar. Matte, lived-in finish — undone but intentional. No fade; the contrast comes from front-to-back length difference.',
