  '640': 'The Winnfield: distinctive disconnected chin curtain / jaw-following beard with moustache, retro bold statement style.',
  '651': 'Extended Goatee (Hollywoodian): moustache plus beard on chin and along the jaw, cheeks shaved high, connected chin-to-jaw, masculine and broad.',
